  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p&gt;The proposed first floor side extension, with particular reference to its excessive width and closing of the gap between the detached dwellings, which forms an important part of the open character within the locality, is considered an incongruous, poor quality and cramped design that fails to integrate with the property overall and the surrounding pattern of development. This is considered contrary to the high-quality design aspirations of the National Planning Policy Framework (2023), Policy D3 Policy of the London Plan (2021); CS.1 of the Harrow Core Strategy (2012), Policy DM1 of the Development Management Plan Local Policies (2013) and the adopted Supplementary Planning Document: Residential Design Guide (2010).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;"
